reviewText:
What a great video this is with one of the greatest traders alive.  Oliver in his classic well articulated manner goes through every thing you need to know about trading short term time frames in order to achieve great profits.  These strategies are focused on the 1-2 day holding period.  Most of these techniques can deliver 80% + wins.  This is a video that one will want to watch over and over again and will learn more each viewing.

I want to thank the seller Planck Time for the fast shipping that arrived before the expected date and in time for my weekend viewing.  The video quality was very good and professional.  I would definitely consider buying from Planck Time again in the future, especially since they sell many other great items as well.
Mr. Velez has a great way he delivers his  knowledge. I recommend to all interested.
